    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is suitable for someone looking for a functional car at a lower price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows significant signs of use, including noticeable exterior scratches, some paint fading, and a well-worn interior with visible staining on the upholstery. Mechanically, it is reliable for daily commutes, but it may require some minor repairs or maintenance in the near future, such as suspension work or addressing slow leaks. It is a solid, honest car for a buyer who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
