    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles high-torque loads without fatigue. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, and the braking system provides consistent modulation. While the paint exhibits minor road-going patina, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in excellent mechanical health, offering a visceral, analog performance profile.",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
