    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-loved and consistently maintained driver. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats show only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all interior electronics\u2014including the navigation system and heated seats\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of performance tires installed just 3,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. It offers a perfect balance for a buyer who wants a premium experience and mechanical peace of mind without the steep depreciation of a showroom-new model.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
